10485	Pegasus Gold Inc said milling operations have started at its Montana Tunnels open-pit gold silver zinc and lead mine near Helena The start-up is three months ahead of schedule and six mln dlrs under budget the company said Original capital cost of the mine was 575 mln dlrs but came in at 515 mln dlrs the company said After a start-up period the mill is expected to produce 106000 ounces of gold 1700000 ounces of silver 26000 tons of zinc and 5700 tons of lead on an annual basis from 4300000 tons of ore the company said
